# WHAT WE FED Guardrails

- This is a repo workflow / agent capability pass unless user explicitly expands scope.
- Do not modify gameplay systems, scene flow, or balance during agent-layer tasks.
- Do not widen into ranch, world-state, kaiju, or unrelated gameplay expansion.
- Do not reintroduce stale pause-era assumptions.

# Preserve Locked Core

- Timing truth and lane readability are non-negotiable.
- Support readability and telegraph clarity are protected.
- DNA meaning and Bond vs Eat tension remain meaningful.
- No-pause applies during active combat; between-level menus are allowed by design.

# Working Style

- Prefer explicit anti-drift decisions over generic optimization.
- Keep changes surgical and explain non-goals.
